-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Parser Auto Require - A rich declarative webapp using auto-require
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Authors: Kitson P. Kelly
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Demo description

	A rich webapp fully leveraging declarative markup and minimising the amount 
	of modules initially loaded, therefore using the auto-require feature of 
	the parser when required.
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

	Dojo Core
	dijit
	dojox

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions

	Run the included demo.html
		
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
